    },
    {
      "id": "d4",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 100,
      "text": "This message indicates you haven't loaded any .xcanvas files into the PingCanvas web folder.\n\n1. Open the editor (index.html) and draw your network - or File → Load Sample.\n2. Add an IP address to each device you want monitored. (Device Details)\n3. Save, and place the file as board.xcanvas in the data folder\nWindows: C:\\PingCanvas\\web\nDocker: ./data\nIIS: Site Root (e.g. C:\\inetpub\\wwwroot )\n4. Make sure the poller is running:\nDocker: docker compose up \nWindows: Check scheduled task\nThe poller pings your devices and writes the results back to a status file.\nOnce the poller has started and a .xcanvas in place, refresh this page.",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontColor": "#000000",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "lineFormats": [
        {
          "bold": true,
          "italic": false
        },
        {
